videoDetails.Title: How to Create Desmos Art 1  Lines and Circles  Step by Step Guide
videoDetails.Description:
If you enjoy playing around with functions and graphs, you might be interested in the so-called Desmos Art. You can create a whole bunch of creative artworks like logos, patterns, pictures, cartoon characters and portraits by only using DESMOS Graphing Calculator. In this video, you can learn the basics, most important features of creating desmos art. I will record more videos about desmos and share all my experience soon.
